c: 18
v: 21
t: "And thus We made people to stumble upon them (the Men of the Cave) that they (people) might know — when they quarrelled among themselves in their affair — that Allah's promise is true and that there is no doubt about the Hour. And they (the people who came to know the story of the Men of the Cave) said, \"Erect a monument over them.\" Their Lord is well aware of them. Those who had authority over people's affairs said, \"We will certainly raise a place of worship over them"